iblocksync (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * [Fixed] #2: Don't attempt to truncate block devices.
  * [Fixed] WritableBlockImage: Properly calculate file size while modifying an image.
  * [Fixed] Allow syncing images with a non-divisible block size.
  * [New] Add log message when truncating target image.
  * [New] Improve error handling.

